{"tid":365434,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★假難民鬧市揮刀欲斬途人","createTime":"2017-08-19T08:34:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-19T13:22:12.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5fb7ff307d57866f956f9e5855db19046b500a5d","tid":365434,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T08:34:32.000Z","msg":"油麻地廟街108-236號對開，下午3時18分發生假難民與警員刀槍對峙事件。一名非洲漢疑情緒不穩，突擸刀在街上揮舞，圖向途人施襲，途人見狀報案。西九龍衝鋒隊第3隊警員接報趕至，持盾牌戒備，惟非洲漢仍情緒激動，一名便裝警見警告無效，即時拔槍對峙及喝止，數名警員迅即將男子按地制服及拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170819/photo/bkn-20170819153445818-0819_00822_001_03b.jpg?20170819163017\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170819%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170819153445818-0819_00822_001_03b.jpg%3F20170819163017&h=f8e5b893&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170819/bkn-20170819153445818-0819_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170819%2Fbkn-20170819153445818-0819_00822_001.html&d=x2IW1bC65jmE8rtUN4lwW9ibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=fc3a2d6a\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170819/bkn-20170819153445818-0819_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"5167e915b4ae9266416ecefefe36c5c39f5d1a82","tid":365434,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T08:35:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=54o5CvdpzZ0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D54o5CvdpzZ0&d=x2IW1bC65jmE8rtUN4lwW9ibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=26d44136\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=54o5CvdpzZ0</a>"},{"pid":"a24495d378599bd82ee2c8927ae132f2df06b610","tid":365434,"uid":130513,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T08:40:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"50bb906ca95664baec075b08e7720fd2e3959619","tid":365434,"uid":40272,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"ci